            <p>In addition to this, we've gave you more control over your data. Our policy explains how you can make choices about your information.</a></p>
            <p>These updates will take effect on May 25, 2018 and by using HorseSpot on or after that date, you'll be agreeing to the above changes.</p>
            <p>For any further assistance, please write to us at <a href="mailto:contact@horse-spot.com">contact@horse-spot.com.</a></p>
            <p>Best regards, <br /> HorseSpot Team</p>
        </div><!-- text -->

        <footer class="footer">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/horsespotcom/" target="_blank"><img src="https://www.horse-spot.com/assets/images/facebook_share.png" alt="Facebook Icon"></a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/horsespotcom" target="_blank"><img src="https://www.horse-spot.com/assets/images/ig_share.png" alt="Instagram Icon"></a></li>
                <li><a href="https://twitter.com/horsespotcom" target="_blank"><img src="https://www.horse-spot.com/assets/images/tw_share.png" alt="Twitter Icon"></a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-K5relSxxR0yBu-OOi9XQg" target="_blank"><img src="https://www.horse-spot.com/assets/images/yt_share.png" alt="YouTube Icon"></a></li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://www.horse-spot.com" target="_blank">www.horse-spot.com</a>
            <a href="mailto:contact@horse-spot.com" target="_blank">contact@horse-spot.com</a>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>


